{"tid":2253618,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"男星Michael Rooker宣佈擊敗武漢肺炎：唔靠藥物","createTime":"2020-10-22T09:24:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-22T10:38:33.000Z","uid":181997,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6350caf8e89a5bcaff6b119ac4d5fced6cb885b4","tid":2253618,"uid":181997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T09:24:32.000Z","msg":"在Marvel超級英雄電影《銀河守護隊》（Guardians of the Galaxy）飾演「破壞者」領袖勇度的65歲男星Michael Rooker，上周五在FB透露早前確診武漢肺炎，並且已經打勝仗。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/45lgNMrV1ca2argN1El9wVmSYOE=/720x405/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TVQG33EQYZGHPCBLT7ROLAGYMY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F45lgNMrV1ca2argN1El9wVmSYOE%3D%2F720x405%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTVQG33EQYZGHPCBLT7ROLAGYMY.jpg&h=b1e632dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nMichael在FB公開最新的武肺檢驗報告，已經對病毒呈陰性反應。他留言：「我需要讓你們知道，這是一場激戰。就如所有戰爭一樣，都是公平的。在這場漫長而艱難的戰爭中，我得出一個結論，當病毒一進入了你的體內，不是很多人能夠靠外在的幫助打贏武肺。這只是我的見解，肯定不是科學研究的結論。真正的戰爭是在裏面，是細胞的層面。」Michael又指：「對我來說，我決定不服用藥物或維化命。我覺得如果我的免疫系統在還未準備好打仗時，再加入額外的東西，只會損害腎和肝。在與武肺戰鬥的過程中，我看到每日戰爭的結果，不是覺得很糟糕就是覺得還不錯，事實上是半個人的狀態。我只是想告訴你們我打勝仗了！武肺雖然打得算不錯，但最終都被我的免疫系統擊敗！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/N4nqTY7NSpw6KHfDmHCC_4-kBxk=/1200x600/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/IAFMM3WI6JETTFICHZANNVQDOU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FN4nqTY7NSpw6KHfDmHCC_4-kBxk%3D%2F1200x600%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FIAFMM3WI6JETTFICHZANNVQDOU.jpg&h=08a9352a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/fz3AQ1GNMwkUX7KxrfHMg8sEizc=/490x490/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/H6TQF6EIGRC65HKQ24URMK5CCM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Ffz3AQ1GNMwkUX7KxrfHMg8sEizc%3D%2F490x490%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FH6TQF6EIGRC65HKQ24URMK5CCM.jpg&h=bbaa4249&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"57b5945a89dc281307691e247fd63802fea1a450","tid":2253618,"uid":181997,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T09:31:02.000Z","msg":"唔食藥都可以好返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7c0835bb08f4451d7f9455e14f9659b50565ac4","tid":2253618,"uid":29299,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T09:32:44.000Z","msg":"有無可能假陰性..<br />\n希望佢之後無事"},{"pid":"336d96c2208eba23f729b3212a9a212955bececf","tid":2253618,"uid":181997,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d7c0835bb08f4451d7f9455e14f9659b50565ac4","tid":2253618,"uid":29299,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T09:32:44.000Z","msg":"有無可能假陰性..<br />\n希望佢之後無事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T09:34:33.000Z","msg":"應該好番晒，因為都成個月前<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eeaff321aeac880398e56c4440dcf273d24cce9","tid":2253618,"uid":155431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T09:36:57.000Z","msg":"跳唔跳得過1cm先<br />\n<br />\n幫連登仔問"},{"pid":"9e4d1063aaa671ac7d05b5919c9f26e0a14f381a","tid":2253618,"uid":181997,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3eeaff321aeac880398e56c4440dcf273d24cce9","tid":2253618,"uid":155431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T09:36:57.000Z","msg":"跳唔跳得過1cm先<br />\n<br />\n幫連登仔問"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T09:42:58.000Z","msg":"你問吓佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/officialmichaelrooker/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.faceboo